comment: The enzyme accepts the vancomycin and teicoplanin pseudoaglycone as substrate. The substrate tolerance may be even broader than the largest common substructure between vancomycin and teicoplanin.

changelog.comment: Initial entry. Reviewer 1 reworked reaction SMARTS to allow for a balanced reaction. Reviewer 2 changed text of enzyme description and enzyme reaction description
Adjusted reaction depiction to implement editorial guidelines (no depiction of non-covalent bound cofactors).

reactions.description: Transfers vancosamine onto glucose on hpg4 of vancomycin pseudoaglycone.
